  <entry>
    <title>GitHub Pages with Hexo</title>
    <link href="/2022/03/31/GitHub%20Pages%20with%20Hexo%20tips/"/>
    <url>/2022/03/31/GitHub%20Pages%20with%20Hexo%20tips/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="基础部分"><a href="#基础部分" class="headerlink" title="基础部分"></a>基础部分</h2><p>常用指令：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ hexo generate <span class="hljs-comment"># 生成静态文件</span><br>$ hexo serve <span class="hljs-comment"># 启动服务器</span><br>$ hexo deploy <span class="hljs-comment"># 部署网站</span><br>$ hexo clean <span class="hljs-comment"># 清除缓存文件 (db.json) 和已生成的静态文件 (public)</span><br>$ hexo new [layout] &lt;title&gt; <span class="hljs-comment"># 新建一篇文章</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>参考：<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/commands">官方文档</a></p><h2 id="主题"><a href="#主题" class="headerlink" title="主题"></a>主题</h2><p>我这里使用的主题是fluid<a href="https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid">(hexo-theme-fluid)</a>。</p><h2 id="问题"><a href="#问题" class="headerlink" title="问题"></a>问题</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ ERROR Deployer not found: git <span class="hljs-comment"># question</span><br>$ npm install hexo-deployer-git –save <span class="hljs-comment"># solution</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="技巧"><a href="#技巧" class="headerlink" title="技巧"></a>技巧</h2><p>VS Code预览Markdown快捷键：Ctrl+Shirt+V</p><p>教程：<a href="https://hans2936.github.io/">博客</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
    <categories>
      
      <category>Hexo</category>
      
    </categories>
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>森林公园游记</title>
    <link href="/2021/12/05/%E6%A3%AE%E6%9E%97%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%AD%E6%B8%B8%E8%AE%B0/"/>
    <url>/2021/12/05/%E6%A3%AE%E6%9E%97%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%AD%E6%B8%B8%E8%AE%B0/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>来华科已经是第五个年头了，但这却是我第一次在森林公园野餐，和好朋友们度过了一个愉快地下午。以后我应该也会经常来这儿走走，亲近大自然，休息眼睛。<br>备注：从韵苑那里的小路可直达森林公园，总共用时不超过半刻钟！</p><div align="center">  <img src="https://lsh-hexo-image.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image/life/%E5%90%88%E5%BD%B11.jpeg" width="700"/> </div><br><div align="center">  <img src="https://lsh-hexo-image.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image/life/%E5%90%88%E5%BD%B12.jpeg" width="700"/> </div><br>]]></content>
    
    
